		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Zone diet</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b>Zone diet</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Dieting" title="Dieting">diet</a> popularized in books by <a href="/wiki/Biochemist" title="Biochemist">biochemist</a> <a href="/wiki/Barry_Sears" title="Barry Sears">Barry Sears</a>. It advocates consuming calories from carbohydrates, protein and fat in a fixed ratio.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
